{"tid":174802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滙豐爆裁員消息 今向IT部派大信封","createTime":"2017-03-27T05:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T05:54:06.000Z","uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0cccfb9e7e10be0eaa8468abf6c5639ea7cfe10","tid":174802,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:40:37.000Z","msg":"03月27日(一) 11:29<br />\n<br />\n滙豐今日爆裁員消息，香港銀行業僱員協會總幹事陳勇華證實，今早有在總部上班的後勤資訊科技部(IT)員工收到「大信封」，但未知涉及員工人數、裁減模式等具體情況。 <br />\n<br />\n據內部員工消息，IT部員工近日收到通知，要求大部分員工返回公司，至今早有員工證實收到「大信封」。 <br />\n<br />\n截至去年底，香港區人手按年減少1,000人至2.9萬人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170327/bkn-20170327112957058-0327_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170327%2Fbkn-20170327112957058-0327_00842_001.html&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=2a593c27\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170327/bkn-20170327112957058-0327_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/2d/It-dog.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20160705155901\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F2d%2FIt-dog.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20160705155901&h=d30d15fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOb87y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOb87y.png&h=59d0b65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.dcyan.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160315/1458027694944797.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcyan.com%2Fueditor%2Fphp%2Fupload%2Fimage%2F20160315%2F1458027694944797.jpg&h=09bf50e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/58q3gO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F58q3gO.png&h=6a823526&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"874412b258d1432b8891421fa3923c8fe3bc7abb","tid":174802,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:41:35.000Z","msg":"IT狗幅圖好似少緊某一幅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d3cc908c7b29ef82b282b5f26487ed6359f474","tid":174802,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:42:09.000Z","msg":"炒走廿人根本對業績係毫冇建樹<br />\n炒房賺錢少應該炒走班Trader先"},{"pid":"764706e5c57c074dbcbb77676f4a48ad730bab2b","tid":174802,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"仲未計俾人迫走個D。呢間垃圾公司，分工細到無倫，轉工通知期要成三個月，高層視香港後勤為負累，搬哂去印度大陸"},{"pid":"2f2355df6affb57f34af72d2e1da78791d50fb46","tid":174802,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:42:40.000Z","msg":"我唔明it部成日第一批比人裁, 但點解炒極都仲有咁多人?"},{"pid":"1f1fdf1d75d4e6371615f0c41131d32f60a1027f","tid":174802,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:49:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d4ccbdac98604d5b699143839d267c666849e94","tid":174802,"uid":3510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我唔明it部成日第一批比人裁, 但點解炒極都仲有咁多人?</blockquote><br />\n炒完12000嘅人<br />\n用9000請新人</blockquote><br />\n炒完香港 去支那印度請廉價勞工"}]}